          "trigger": "LEL reading above 10% at any point during active hot work or in a permit-required space",
          "action": "refuse",
          "handoffTarget": "ehs_manager",
          "rationale": "10% LEL is the universally applied stop-work threshold; work must halt and cannot resume until the source is found and continuous monitoring re-clears the atmosphere."
        },
